### Problem19


- We use the term _____(0)\___("linear", "quadratic", "cubic", "logarithmic", "linearithmic", "exponential" ) to describe programs whose running time for a problem of size n has order of growth n log n.
- A typical program whose running time has order of growth quadratic (n^2) has double nested "for" _____(1)\___ , used for some calculation involving all parts of n elements.
